*pharo-3.0 (17 Dec 2014)

  17 Dec 2014; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> +pharo-3.0.ebuild:
  version bump

  01 Aug 2013; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> pharo-2.0.ebuild:
  fixed typo in the instructions.

  01 Aug 2013; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> pharo-2.0.ebuild:
  switched from squeakvm to pharovm.
  squeakvm is missing some primitives

  31 Jul 2013; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> pharo-2.0.ebuild:
  Add pharo-2.0

*pharo-1.4-r1 (07 Mar 2013)

  07 Mar 2013; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> +pharo-1.4-r1.ebuild:
  Added dependency to pharo-sources

*pharo-1.4 (06 Mar 2013)

  06 Mar 2013; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> +pharo-1.4.ebuild:
  Version bump

*pharo-1.3-r4 (29 Jan 2012)

  29 Jan 2012; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> +pharo-1.3-r4.ebuild:
  Changed install directory to /usr/share/pharo

*pharo-1.3-r3 (23 Oct 2011)

  23 Oct 2011; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> +pharo-1.3-r3.ebuild:
  Fixed a typo in the squeakvm version.

*pharo-1.3-r2 (23 Oct 2011)

  23 Oct 2011; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> +pharo-1.3-r2.ebuild:
  Add the creation of a symbolic link to PharoV10.sources, to make setting up
  Pharo easier.

*pharo-1.3-r1 (15 Oct 2011)

  15 Oct 2011; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> +pharo-1.3-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed ebuild install bugs

*pharo-1.3 (15 Oct 2011)

  15 Oct 2011; <emmanuel@gentoo.org> +pharo-1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump to 1.3

*pharo-1.2.2 (01 May 2011)

